name: HER FIRST CIGARETTE
description:
On the evening of her 18th birthday Miku tried her first cigarette.

As she sat in her dark and cold bedroom alone, smoking quietly, she felt like she was being watched.

After smoking three cigarettes back to back, Miku finally fell asleep, and began to dream... 

... of a surreal twilight wasteland... 

where diseased and deformed creatures roamed in packs...

... looking for any remaining survivors to feed upon.

Then she woke up.
